{"tid":714220,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［盲毛］其實有冇可能25歲先黎有近視","createTime":"2018-06-23T13:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T04:33:25.000Z","uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43977d2e4526f9b3e86b808657c11c5641e3751f","tid":714220,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"其實小學身體檢查果陣巳經比姑娘話過再唔注意可能要戴眼鏡。<br />\n之後一路無理佢。<br />\n去到上個禮拜，我開始發現我連幾米外路上路人把傘個圖案都睇唔清楚（同我一齊行果個四眼同事睇得好清楚，仲叫我戴眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n我淨係搵左啲online test 黎做，check 到我有75 度近視（做左6次，2次50度，1次100度，仲有3次75度）<br />\n<br />\n我而家諗緊我係咪有需要去驗下眼，但我又覺得平日日常生活都無咩影響，而且真係好似唔係好深度數，專登去驗又好似誇張左少少"},{"pid":"dbde00711f762fcad7b861148c594f1b23a1e26e","tid":714220,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"有 我20歲之後開始近視 依加已經400百度"},{"pid":"88e2795b51de5d8249fcf8e3913bf1c956ca212d","tid":714220,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"我都係 不過係散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bd34fd5546cffdf6730a488cf62277e607c42f","tid":714220,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"75好少事姐<br />\n<br />\n不過我兩隻眼個度數都唔一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左眼 &lt;10度<br />\n右眼 &lt;100度"},{"pid":"8e885729438c06bc18edbea0ee6f6108cb3ef350","tid":714220,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8bd34fd5546cffdf6730a488cf62277e607c42f","tid":714220,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"75好少事姐<br />\n<br />\n不過我兩隻眼個度數都唔一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左眼 &lt;10度<br />\n右眼 &lt;100度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"你有專登去驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/